passages.text:
Oh look, it's the stranger again! Did ya come here to nose around again just like your little friend?
[[Have you seen Sofia anywhere?|Have you seen her]]

links.name: Have you seen Sofia anywhere?|Have you seen her
links.link: Have you seen Sofia anywhere?|Have you seen her

passages.name: Start

passages.text:
I'm assuming that's the name of that so-called "author" girl who was hanging around here for a few weeks? Then no, I haven't seen her today. I don't care to.
[[continue]]
passages.name: Have you seen her

passages.text:
She was trying to get all into everyone's business, which I did not appreciate. You can't just come into a town and act like you're owed answers for something you know nothin' about! I'm glad she left.
[[How did she leave?|How leave]]
passages.name: continue

passages.text:
She coulda swam away, for all I care. All that matters is she's gone, and now the festival can go on in peace.
[[You seem to really hate her...|Hate her]]
[[I'm going to get back to fishing.|bye]]

links.name: You seem to really hate her...|Hate her
links.link: You seem to really hate her...|Hate her

links.name: I'm going to get back to fishing.|bye
links.link: I'm going to get back to fishing.|bye

passages.name: How leave

passages.text:
What are you insinuating? She left of her own accord. She hired a private boat to take her off the island. Said she was too used to fancy city life to withstand our more "unrefined" ways...
[[That doesn't sound like her.|Doesnt sound]]
[[I thought boats were forbidden before the festival?|forbidden boats]]

links.name: That doesn't sound like her.|Doesnt sound
links.link: That doesn't sound like her.|Doesnt sound

links.name: I thought boats were forbidden before the festival?|forbidden boats
links.link: I thought boats were forbidden before the festival?|forbidden boats

passages.name: Hate her

passages.text: Yeah, well, don't let me stop you...
passages.name: bye

passages.text:
How long did you know her for? Two days? What do you know? She was a stranger, and she had no business being here during the festival without participating. It's no wonder she couldn't hack it.
[[I'm going to get back to fishing.|bye]]

links.name: I'm going to get back to fishing.|bye
links.link: I'm going to get back to fishing.|bye

passages.name: Doesnt sound

passages.text:
Well... They are. But she hired a sailboat, so no engine to disturb the wildlife. Besides, we all wanted her gone so bad, none of us were going to object.
[[I'm going to get back to fishing.|bye]]
